@startuml Booking_Saga_Sequence
title Booking Saga - Диаграмма последовательности (happy path)

participant "Пассажир" as passenger
participant "Booking Service (Orchestrator)" as booking #LightBlue
participant "Fraud Service" as fraud
participant "Pricing Service" as pricing
participant "Geography Service" as geography
participant "Driver Service" as driver
participant "Notification Service" as notification

passenger -> booking: Создать заказ
activate booking

== Шаг 1: Создание бронирования ==
booking -> booking: CreateBookingCmd (статус: PENDING)

== Шаги 2-4: Параллельная проверка (оптимизация) ==
booking ->> fraud: CheckBookingFraudCmd
activate fraud
booking ->> pricing: CalculatePriceCmd
activate pricing
booking ->> geography: CalculateRouteCmd
activate geography

fraud --> booking: FraudCheckPassed (risk_score: 0.05)
deactivate fraud
pricing --> booking: PriceCalculated (price: 450₽, surge: 1.2x)
deactivate pricing
geography --> booking: RouteCalculated (ETA: 12 мин, distance: 8.3 км)
deactivate geography

== Шаг 5: Поиск водителя ==
booking -> driver: FindDriverCmd ("умное" перераспределение)
activate driver
note right of driver
  Scoring: расстояние +
  прогноз спроса +
  surge + рейтинг
end note
driver --> booking: DriverAssigned (driver_id, ETA: 4 мин)
deactivate driver

== Шаг 6: Уведомление (async, не блокирует) ==
booking ->> notification: NotifyPartiesCmd
activate notification
notification --> notification: Push пассажиру + Push водителю
deactivate notification

== Шаг 7: Подтверждение ==
booking -> booking: BookingConfirmed

booking --> passenger: Заказ подтвержден (водитель через 4 мин)
deactivate booking

@enduml
